    "finalText": "I don’t have a documented help article for commitments yet.\n\nWhat I can tell you:\n- I searched the app help center first, and there isn’t currently a published workflow for **creating a commitment**.\n- So I’m not going to guess at exact button names or screen flow if the product doc isn’t there.\n\nBest next move:\n- If you want, I can still help in one of two ways:\n  1. **Walk you through the likely workflow** based on the commitments tools available in the app, or\n  2. **Flag this as missing documentation** so the team adds a proper help article for “Create a commitment.”\n\nWhat I do know from the platform capabilities:\n- Commitments in this app cover **subcontracts and purchase orders**.\n- I can also help once you know the target:\n  - “Create a subcontract with [vendor] for [project]”\n  - “Set up a PO for [vendor/material] on [project]”\n\nIf you want the practical version now, tell me:\n- **subcontract or PO**\n- **project name**\n- **vendor/company**\n- **amount**\n- **scope/description**\n\nand I’ll help you structure it cleanly."
